able to be OK with that,

00:48:13.650 --> 00:48:16.640
but being able to move into
really deep conversation

00:48:16.640 --> 00:48:19.670
and dialogue with deep trust
and respect to one another.

00:48:23.845 --> 00:48:25.720
PHIL YU: In talking
