accomplishing anything, right?

00:57:05.270 --> 00:57:08.840
It's like criticizing the voice
that it comes from where you're

00:57:08.840 --> 00:57:10.850
saying like this
person gets to be Asian

00:57:10.850 --> 00:57:14.450
and this person does not is like
what good does that do anybody?

00:57:14.450 --> 00:57:17.060
Honestly.

00:57:17.060 --> 00:57:20.840
I am really an
opponent of people

00:57:20.840 --> 00:57:24.980
who are policing Asian
American identities.

00:57:24.980 --> 00:57:27.200
Asian American identities
